Package: pseudobibeR.es
Title: Aggregate Counts of Spanish Linguistic Features
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Maximiliano",
           family = "Cordovez",
           email = "maximiliano.cf@outlook.es",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates lexicogrammatical and functional features for
    Spanish texts following the framework introduced by Biber (1985)
    <doi:10.1515/ling.1985.23.2.337>. Provides a companion implementation
    to the English-focused 'pseudobibeR' package, including data sets and
    helper utilities tailored to Spanish parsing resources.
